✔ Clear modular separation

api/ → serving layer (FastAPI)

training/ → ML lifecycle code

rag/ → retrieval + LLM reasoning

preprocessing/ → data prep + feature engineering

utils/ → shared helpers + validators

models/ → persisted artifacts

✔ CI/CD ready

GitHub Actions pipeline inside:

.github/workflows/ci_cd.yml

✔ Deployment-ready

Dockerfile, DEPLOYMENT.md, .env.example provide real-world deployment patterns.




